    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ProductId], [t].[ProductName], [t].[FinalPrice], [t].[RegisterOpenTime], [t].[RegisterClosedTime], [t].[OpenTime], [t].[ClosedTime], [t].[Code], [t].[Description], [t].[Active], [t].[Search], [t].[CreatedTime], [t].[ProductProvince], [t].[ProvinveId], [t].[AuctionProductBrand], [t].[AuctionProductCategory], [t].[AuctionProductCategoryId], [t].[AuctionProductBrandId], [t].[AuctionProductStatusName], [t].[AuctionProductStatusId], [t].[flagOrdered], [t].[orderId]
    FROM (
        SELECT [a].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [ProductId], [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a].[FinalPrice], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [a].[Code], [a].[Description], [a].[Active], [a].[Search], [a].[CreatedTime], [p0].[Name] AS [ProductProvince], [p0].[Id] AS [ProvinveId], [p1].[Name] AS [AuctionProductBrand], [p2].[Name] AS [AuctionProductCategory], [p2].[Id] AS [AuctionProductCategoryId], [p].[ProductBrandId] AS [AuctionProductBrandId], [a0].[Name] AS [AuctionProductStatusName], [a].[AuctionProductStatusId], CASE
            WHEN EXISTS (
                SELECT 1
                FROM [Orders] AS [o]
                WHERE [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS [flagOrdered], COALESCE((
            SELECT TOP(1) [o0].[Id]
            FROM [Orders] AS [o0]
            WHERE [o0].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]), 0) AS [orderId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]

    ) AS [t]
    UNION ALL

                FROM [Orders] AS [o]
                WHERE [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a1].[Id]) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS [flagOrdered], COALESCE((

            ELSE 0

    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ProductId], [t].[ProductName], [t].[FinalPrice], [t].[RegisterOpenTime], [t].[RegisterClosedTime], [t].[OpenTime], [t].[ClosedTime], [t].[Code], [t].[Description], [t].[Active], [t].[Search], [t].[CreatedTime], [t].[ProductProvince], [t].[ProvinveId], [t].[AuctionProductBrand], [t].[AuctionProductCategory], [t].[AuctionProductCategoryId], [t].[AuctionProductBrandId], [t].[AuctionProductStatusName], [t].[AuctionProductStatusId], [t].[flagOrdered], [t].[orderId]
    FROM (
        SELECT [a].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [ProductId], [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a].[FinalPrice], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [a].[Code], [a].[Description], [a].[Active], [a].[Search], [a].[CreatedTime], [p0].[Name] AS [ProductProvince], [p0].[Id] AS [ProvinveId], [p1].[Name] AS [AuctionProductBrand], [p2].[Name] AS [AuctionProductCategory], [p2].[Id] AS [AuctionProductCategoryId], [p].[ProductBrandId] AS [AuctionProductBrandId], [a0].[Name] AS [AuctionProductStatusName], [a].[AuctionProductStatusId], CASE
            WHEN EXISTS (
                SELECT 1
                FROM [Orders] AS [o]
                WHERE [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS [flagOrdered], COALESCE((
            SELECT TOP(1) [o0].[Id]
            FROM [Orders] AS [o0]
            WHERE [o0].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]), 0) AS [orderId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
        WHERE (([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND (([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0))
    ) AS [t]
    UNION ALL

        INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
        WHERE (([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND (([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0))
    ) AS [t]
    UNION ALL
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[FinalPrice], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[Code], [t1].[Description], [t1].[Active], [t1].[Search], [t1].[CreatedTime], [t1].[ProductProvince], [t1].[ProvinveId], [t1].[AuctionProductBrand], [t1].[AuctionProductCategory], [t1].[AuctionProductCategoryId], [t1].[AuctionProductBrandId], [t1].[AuctionProductStatusName], [t1].[AuctionProductStatusId], [t1].[flagOrdered], [t1].[orderId]
    FROM (

            WHEN EXISTS (
                SELECT 1
                FROM [Orders] AS [o]
                WHERE [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a1].[Id]) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS [flagOrdered], COALESCE((
            SELECT TOP(1) [o0].[Id]
            FROM [Orders] AS [o0]
            WHERE [o0].[AuctionProductId] = [a1].[Id]), 0) AS [orderId], [p5].[Id] AS [Id0], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p3] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p3].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p4] ON [p3].[ProvinceId] = [p4].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p5] ON [p3].[ProductBrandId] = [p5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p6] ON [p3].[ProductCategoryId] = [p6].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a2] ON [a1].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a2].[Id]
        WHERE (([a1].[Active] = 1) AND ([p3].[Active] = 1)) AND (([p4].[Id] = 2) AND ([a1].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0))
    ) AS [t1]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o].[FinalPrice], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]

    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2134277 for more information. To identify the query that's triggering this warning call 'ConfigureWarnings(w => w.Throw(RelationalEventId.MultipleCollectionIncludeWarning))'.

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterOpenTime], [t].[RegisterClosedTime], [t].[OpenTime], [t].[ClosedTime], [t].[Name0], [t].[Name1], [t].[Name2], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Username], [t0].[Password], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name3], [t].[Price], [t].[Color], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t].[Note], [t1].[Username], [t1].[Password], [t1].[Description], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[OrderStatusId] = @__DEPOSITED_0)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)) AND ((CONVERT(varchar(11), [o].[OrderStatusId]) LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(CONVERT(varchar(11), [o].[OrderStatusId]), @__fillter_0) > 0))
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

2024-01-02 12:44:14.745 +07:00 [INF] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command
Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]

    WHERE ((((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[OrderStatusId] = @__DEPOSITED_0)) AND ((CONVERT(varchar(11), [o].[OrderStatusId]) LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(CONVERT(varchar(11), [o].[OrderStatusId]), @__fillter_1) > 0))
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]

    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE ((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
